These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, tiparillo, oliveros
There are 3 different nationalities: german, australian, egyptian
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, zinnia, dahlia
City: berlin, london, new-york
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, skateboarding, tennis
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, train, van
 1. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
 2. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
 3. the australian is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 4. the tiparillo-smoker is the person who growszinnia##1
 5. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 6. the australian is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the german is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 8. the person driving the boat is the person traveling to london##1
 9. the oliveros-smoker is between the person traveling to london and the person driving the van##2
10. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4
11. the german is the person traveling to new-york##1
12. the egyptian is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |         2          |     3      |
| Cigar          | bluemaster   | oliveros            | tiparillo     |
| Nationality           | german | egyptian | australian |
| Flower   | bellflower      | dahlia               | zinnia        |
| City           | new-york        | berlin         | london   |
| Sport         | tennis     | skateboarding      | golf       |
| Transport     | van        | train              | boat       |

