.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, january, june
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, singing, writing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, documentary
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, russian, japanese
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, parkour, snowboarding
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, subway, trike
 1. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 3. the russian is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is the indonesian##1
 5. the person driving the trike is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person watching crime movies##2
 6. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person who's hobby is singing and the person driving the skateboard##2
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 8. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left or far right##3
10. the japanese is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |
| Birthday      | december | january | june        |
| Hobby          | singing   | writing    | board-games        |
| Movie-Genre   | crime    | disaster | documentary |
| Nationality   | japanese   | indonesian  | russian         |
| Sport           | snowboarding    | rugby | parkour       |
| Transport     | subway   | trike    | skateboard  |

