.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice, tea
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, disco, house
City: colone, berlin, marseilles
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, entrepreneur, scientist
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, turquise, pink
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, basketball, handball
 1. the chef is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 2. the scientist is the fan of house##1
 3. the person who likes turquise is the person drinking juice##1
 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the fan of funk is between the person traveling to berlin and the person who's sport is basketball##2
 6. the fan of house is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who likes turquise is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3
 9. the scientist is on the far right##1
10. the person traveling to marseilles is in an odd position##4
11. the person traveling to berlin is the entrepreneur##1
12. the person who likes turquise is on the far left##1
13. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3       |
| Beverage      | juice        | 7up     | tea          |
| Music-Genre          | disco     | funk | house    |
| City         | berlin    | colone  | marseilles |
| Job           | entrepreneur | chef    | scientist    |
| Color   | turquise      | pink | white      |
| Sport           | volleyball          | handball     | basketball         |

