.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, aquamarine, turquise
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks, reading
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, manager, bartender
3 different pets are kept: frog, fish, goldfish
There are 3 different nationalities: british, mexican, spanish
House: modern, palace, colonial
 1. the manager is on the right of the bartender##1
 2. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the palace house##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
 5. the owner of the frog is between the palace house and the person who's hobby is reading##2
 6. the mexican is on the far right##1
 7. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person who likes turquise##3
 8. the paramedic is the modern house##1
 9. the british is in an odd position##4
10. the spanish is in an even position##4
11. the mexican is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person who's hobby is reading is the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Color      | aquamarine  | turquise      | brown        |
| Hobby         | reading   | cooking     | magic-tricks |
| Job   | paramedic | bartender | manager     |
| Pet   | fish    | frog         | goldfish         |
| Nationality   | british   | spanish     | mexican      |
| House         | modern  | colonial     | palace         |

