 3. the lawyer is the person driving the roller##1
 4. the architect is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 5. the owner of the hamster is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person eating carrot is on the right of the photographer##1
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is in the middle##1
 8. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
 9. the owner of the lizard is between the person traveling to new-york and the person eating cauliflower##2
10. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1

