House: victorian, farmhouse, futuristic
There 3 different types of food: watermelon, strawberry, kale
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, scooter
 1. the person who likes light-blue is between the person driving the airplane and the person driving the motorbike##2
 2. the victorian house is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
 3. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who likes white##1
 4. the person eating strawberry is the person who likes red##1
 5. the futuristic house is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 6. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
 7. the person eating kale is in an odd position##4
 8. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person eating kale is on the right of the victorian house##1
10. the person eating strawberry is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
12. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3        |
| Flower           | tulip | poppy | amaryllis |
