 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
 8. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4
 9. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
10. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
