.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-18::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, brown, black
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, card-games, hiking
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, peach, pomegranate
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, indie, trance
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, december, march
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, baccarat, ritmeester
1. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the fan of indie is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's birthday is in march##2
3. the person who's birthday is in november is in an odd position##4
4. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
5. the baccarat-smoker is on the far left##1
6. the person eating peach is on the right of the person who likes black##1
7. the fan of d&b is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
8. the siglo-smoker is between the person eating kiwi and the person who likes black##2
9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |         2          |      3      |
| Color      | black    | brown           | purple         |
| Hobby         | hiking   | baking             | card-games  |
| Food           | pomegranate  | peach | kiwi |
| Music-Genre   | d&b      | indie              | trance      |
| Birthday   | march | december             | november     |
| Cigar         | baccarat   | siglo           | ritmeester      |

