.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-19::.
There 3 different types of food: peach, potato, spinach
House: townhouse, gothic-revival, tower
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, emerald, red
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, lily, rose
City: rome, berlin, marseilles
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, roller, scooter
 1. the person who likes aquamarine is in an odd position##4
 2. the person eating spinach is on the left of the tower house##1
 3. the person driving the car is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 4. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3
 5. the person driving the car is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 6. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 7. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
 8. the person who likes red is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 9. the gothic-revival house is the person eating potato##1
10. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |
| Food          | potato    | spinach  | peach   |
| House   | gothic-revival      | townhouse  | tower  |
| Color   | aquamarine | emerald  | red |
| Flower           | lily     | amaryllis   | rose   |
| City         | rome  | berlin | marseilles |
| Transport     | scooter   | car      | roller  |

