.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-20::.
City: liverpool, new-york, rome
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, gardening, woodworking
The people have 3 different jobs:  librarian, mechanic, photographer
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, daisy, rose
3 different games are played: snooker, chess, mah-jongg
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, april, october
 1. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 2. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
 3. the person who growsrose is the person traveling to liverpool##1
 4. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 5. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the photographer is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 8. the librarian is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the mechanic##1
10. the mechanic is the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |
| City          | new-york     | rome   | liverpool     |
| Hobby         | woodworking | collecting   | gardening  |
| Job           | librarian   | photographer | mechanic   |
| Flower   | azalea    | daisy       | rose    |
| Game   | mah-jongg        | snooker    | chess   |
| Birthday         | april      | july     | october |

 